Script,MajorWith2ndSuit
setDealerCode(
`
# Predict South's Opening Suit
s = spades(south)
h = hearts(south)
d = diamonds(south)
c = clubs(south)
oS = s>4 and s>=h and s>=d and s>=c
oH = not oS and h>4 and h>=d and h>=c

# South opens 1H or 1S with a second suit of at least 5-cards
(oS or oH)
and hcp(south)>8 and hcp(south)<16 
and shape(south, any 85xx +any 76xx +any 65xx +any 65xx)

# and North has 12+
and hcp(north)>11

`, "S", true);
Script
Button,Major w/2nd Suit,\n\
--- Major with 2nd Suit\n\
South opens 1!H or 1!S with a second suit of at least 5-cards and North has 12+.\n\
We use game-forcing relay after major opening (GRAMMY)\n\
http://clairebridge.com/textes/karensrules.pdf\n\
%MajorWith2ndSuit%
